\begin_inset Formula $kx=k^{\prime}x=k^{\prime\prime}x$
\end_inset

，导出：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\theta^{\prime}=\theta,\quad\frac{\sin\theta}{\sin\theta^{\prime\prime}}=\frac{\sqrt{\mu_{2}\varepsilon_{2}}}{\sqrt{\mu_{1}\varepsilon_{1}}^{\prime\prime}}=\frac{v_{1}}{v_{2}}=\frac{n_{2}}{n_{1}}
\]

\end_inset

利用界面关系
\begin_inset Formula $\sbf{e}_{n}\times\left(\sbf{E}_{2}-\sbf{E}_{1}\right)=0,\quad\sbf{e}_{n}\times\left(\sbf{H}_{2}-\sbf{H}_{1}\right)=0$
