\begin_inset Formula $\sbf{E}$
\end_inset

垂直于入射面偏振时：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{E_{\perp}^{\prime}}{E_{\perp}}=-\frac{\sin\left(\theta-\theta^{\prime\prime}\right)}{\sin\left(\theta+\theta^{\prime\prime}\right)},\quad\frac{E_{\perp}^{\prime\prime}}{E_{\perp}}=\frac{2\cos\theta\sin\theta^{\prime\prime}}{\sin\left(\theta+\theta^{\prime\prime}\right)},
\]

\end_inset

当
\begin_inset Formula $\sbf{E}$
\end_inset

