\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{E_{\ssl}^{\prime}}{E_{\ssl}}=\frac{\tan\left(\theta-\theta^{\prime\prime}\right)}{\tan\left(\theta+\theta^{\prime\prime}\right)},\quad\frac{E_{\ssl}^{\prime\prime}}{E_{\ssl}}=\frac{2\cos\theta\sin\theta^{\prime\prime}}{\sin\left(\theta+\theta^{\prime\prime}\right)\cos\left(\theta-\theta^{\prime\prime}\right)},
\]

\end_inset

即垂直入射面的波与平行入射面的波在界面上具有不同的折射和反射行为。当
\begin_inset Formula $\theta+\theta^{\prime\prime}=\pi/2$
